Simple demonstration of nCrux Configuration Tool (nct) usage
============================================================

This project demonstrates usage of nCrux Configuration Tool (nct) in terms of
configuration menu, configuration fragment merging, code generation for various
high-level languages.

Use the following instructions to build and test the project.

Configure project based on classic menu.

	$ nct menu

Merge a configuration fragment to main configuration file.

	$ make merge

Generate code for all high-level languges and test them.

	$ make test-all


